high_descs: Move towards the white door, then turn left and move towards the refrigerator, then turn left and move to the range, then turn right and move to the sink to the left of the coffee maker.
Pick up the gold handled knife in front of the black mug from the sink.
Move closer to the window behind the sink.
Slice the apple on the counter to the left of the sink using the knife.
Back slightly away from the sink.
Place the knife in the sink to the right of the black mug.
Move closer to the window behind the sink.
Pick up one apple slice from the left of the sink.
Turn left and face the microwave to the right of the range.

Open the microwave, place the apple slice on the plate between the potato and the egg, then microwave the apple slice, open up the microwave, pick up the apple slice, and then close the microwave door.
Turn left and move to the counter edge opposite of the two yellow chairs.
Place the apple slice on the edge of the counter to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple slice on the counter.

high_descs: Walk forward across the room, turn left and cross the room, then turn left and cross the room and turn to the right to face the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Look up to face the apple to the left of the sink.
Cut the apple on the sink into 3 pieces.
Look down to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Step to the right to face the apple on the counter.
Pick up the piece of apple on the counter.
Turn to the left to face the microwave.
Heat the apple piece in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn left and walk forward to face the counter.
Place the apple piece on the counter.
anns.task_desc: He heat a piece of apple and place it on the counter across from the sink.

high_descs: Walk across the room, turn 90 degrees to the left, turn another 90 degrees to the left, and walk along the counter until you reach the sink.
Take the knife out of the sink.
Turn your head to look upward.
Slice the apple to the left of the sink.
Look back down at the sink.
Put the knife back in the sink.
Turn your head to look upward.
Pick up a slice of the apple.
Turn 90 degrees to the left to face the microwave.
Open the door, put the apple inside, close the door, cook the apple, wait, open the door, take the apple out, and close the door.
Turn to the left 90 degrees and walk towards the counter.
Place the apple on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Cut a apple into a few pieces to place one of them on the counter.
